  speedStat="A missed window installation enquiry can cost you £2,000-8,000."
  speedText="Glazing leads — especially full-house replacements, conservatories, and bi-fold doors — are high-value work. When a homeowner finally decides to get quotes, they call two or three companies. The one who answers first, wins. Rapid Receptionist makes sure that's you."
  scenario="It's a bright Saturday morning. You're fitting a bay window on a semi in Birmingham — scaffolding up, old frame out, new frame halfway in. Your phone buzzes repeatedly. A restaurant owner in Solihull has had his front window smashed overnight and needs emergency boarding before the lunch rush. A couple in Edgbaston want a quote for replacing every window in their 1930s semi — potentially a £6,000 job. A conservatory company needs a subcontractor to install roof panels on a project in Sutton Coldfield, starting Wednesday. You're holding a window in place and can't even reach your phone. Without Rapid Receptionist, the restaurant calls another glazier, the couple get a quote from your competitor, and the subcontract work goes elsewhere. With it, the emergency is escalated to you instantly, and the two high-value leads are captured with full details for your callback."
